messages.subject: RE:Lemony Snicket
messages.msgSnippet: All you L.S. fans do know there s a movie in production, don t you? Jim Carrey as Count Olaf, and the cast also includes Meryl Streep, Emily Browning, Jude
messages.messageBody:
All you L.S. fans do know there's a movie in production, don't you? Jim
Carrey as Count Olaf, and the cast also includes Meryl Streep, Emily
Browning, Jude Law, Liam Aiken and Jennifer Coolidge, according to one fan
board. Apparently it's run into director troubles and the original start
date of holiday 2003 has been pushed back to at least next summer.

Karen
